      • getMomentAndAxes

        IVector[] getMomentAndAxes(IMolecule molecule)
        Returns the moment of inertia as a vector containing Ix, Iy, Iz and also the principle axes. The 0 element is the moment of inertia vector while elements 1, 2 and 3 are the principle axes.
